column6: Hello! I'm JeopardyAgent. Take a minute to introduce yourselves.
i want to learn more about WGU!

Then... You will answer with the question! In this case, it should be: "What is WGU?", or you may simply type: "WGU". Please alternate turns to give everyone an equal chance to play. We will do 8 questions in total!
